{
  "_note": "Vera Example demo data. Expectations for the sibling fixtures; consumed by verify.py reader tests (C3) and migration tool tests (C4). Outcomes and finding codes are defined in docs/learn-bundle-spec.md §9.2. 'findings' lists codes that MUST appear; additional findings MAY appear (e.g. informational duplicate-concept).",
  "cases": [
